@page "/ActivitesToDO"
@using WelcomeToLebanonWebPage.Shared
@inject HttpClient Http

<PageTitle>ActivitesToDO</PageTitle>
<div class="text-activitytodo-design"> 
    <h1>Activites To DO</h1>
    <p class="activityToDo-text">
        1. Explore the historic city of Byblos: Visit ancient ruins, stroll through the charming streets, and enjoy the coastal views.<br />

        <br />

        2. Relax on the pristine beaches of Batroun or Tyre: Enjoy sunbathing, swimming, and water sports in these coastal towns.<br />

        <br />
        3. Take a hike in the stunning Kadisha Valley: Enjoy breathtaking landscapes, visit monasteries, and immerse yourself in nature.<br />

        <br />
        4. Enjoy outdoor activities in the picturesque Chouf Mountains: Go hiking, biking, or simply enjoy a picnic surrounded by scenic beauty.<br />

        <br />

        5. Visit the Roman ruins of Baalbek: Marvel at the majestic temples and ruins of this UNESCO World Heritage site.<br />

        <br />

        6. Explore the picturesque vineyards of the Bekaa Valley: Take a wine tour, taste local wines, and enjoy the beautiful surroundings.<br />
    </p>

</div>




